OL,3,CGladiators star Barney Walsh banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving for speeding in Mercedes
OL,6,FGladiators presenter Barney Walsh has
OL,7,Fbeen banned from driving for six
OL,8,Fmonths after he was caught breaking a
OL,9,Ftemporary 50mph speed limit on a
OL,10,Fmotorway.
OL,12,FThe 28-year-old was behind the wheel
OL,13,Fof his 2023 black Mercedes-Benz SUV
OL,14,Fwhen he was caught driving at 58mph in
OL,15,Fa 50mph stretch of the M4.
OL,17,FThe incident happened on October 27
OL,18,Flast year in south Gloucestershire at
OL,19,Fjunction 19 westbound, where a
OL,20,Ftemporary maximum speed restriction
OL,21,Fwas in place.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
