OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1775740266
OL,3,CGladiators star Barney Walsh banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving for speeding in Mercedes
OL,6,FWalsh, who presents the hit BBC game
OL,7,Fshow alongside his father Bradley, was
OL,8,Fsentenced for the offence at Romford
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe TV star did not attend the court
OL,12,Fhearing due to "work commitments"
OL,13,Fwhich have "taken him out of England
OL,14,Fat the moment", his lawyer Gwyn Lewis
OL,15,Ftold magistrates.
OL,17,FMr Lewis ` who had been instructed by
OL,18,FWalsh to appear on his behalf ` told
OL,19,Fthe court his client had nine points
OL,20,Fon his licence, meaning a
OL,21,Fdisqualification was "inevitable".
OL,26,@tD@POUtD@aO]uD@LOUvD@NO]}D@VOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
