CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1775740266
OL,3,CGladiators star Barney Walsh banned
OL,4,Cfrom driving for speeding in Mercedes
OL,6,F"I'm not instructed to resist the
OL,7,Fdisqualification and he has been told
OL,8,Fhe is not to drive from last night,"
OL,9,FMr Lewis added.
OL,11,FWalsh previously pleaded guilty to one
OL,12,Fcount of exceeding a temporary 50mph
OL,13,Fspeed restriction on a motorway.
OL,15,FChairwoman of the magistrates' bench
OL,16,FJanis Sanders banned Walsh from
OL,17,Fdriving for six months.
OL,19,FHe was also ordered to pay a fixed
OL,20,Fpenalty notice of #72, surcharge of
OL,21,F#28 and prosecution costs of #85.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]
